# Gmail setup instructions:
# 1. Create free Gmail account for testing
# 2. Go to Google Cloud Console (console.cloud.google.com)
# 3. Create new project or use existing
# 4. Enable Gmail API
# 5. Create OAuth2 credentials (Desktop Application)
# 6. Download credentials.json file
# 7. Add your Google API key above
# 8. Run: python gmail_manager.py

# The script will handle OAuth2 authentication automatically
# No need to store Gmail password here - OAuth2 is more secure
